        <h2>Overview of MECEE-BL 2026</h2>
        <p>The Medical Education Commission (MEC) conducts the Common Entrance Examination for Bachelor Level programs (MECEE-BL). The third revision (April 28, 2026) emphasizes PCB foundation and norm-referenced evaluation.</p>

        <h2>Eligibility Criteria (Group I - MBBS, BDS, BSc Nursing etc.)</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>10+2 Science (PCB) with 50% aggregate or GPA 2.4</li>
            <li>Or equivalent Health Science Diploma with 50% and equivalence certificate</li>
        </ul>

